      "description": "This vehicle is in fair condition and would make a dependable daily driver for someone who isn't concerned with perfection. The exterior shows its age with some noticeable paint fading on the roof and hood, along with a few minor scuffs and small dings around the fenders. Inside, the cabin is intact but shows typical wear, including some thinning upholstery on the driver\u2019s side and minor staining on the rear floor mats. While the engine and transmission are running smoothly, the vehicle will likely require new tires and a routine brake service within the next few months to remain in top shape.",
