    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_4_listing_4",
      "firm_id": "sybil_4",
      "description": "Presenting a truly exceptional find: a vehicle that looks and drives as if it just rolled off the showroom floor. This car has been meticulously garage-kept and pampered, with every service performed ahead of schedule. The exterior paint retains its deep, mirror-like factory luster, entirely free of stone chips, swirls, or door dings. Inside, the cabin is a pristine sanctuary; the premium leather seats show no bolster wear, the carpets are spotless, and every electronic feature functions with factory-new precision. Mechanically, it is beyond reproach\u2014the engine delivers effortless power while the transmission shifts with seamless fluidity. From the immaculate engine bay to the clean undercarriage, this is a collector-grade example that will satisfy the most discerning enthusiast seeking perfection.",
      "price": 48500.0,
